<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-autospace:none"><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;FreightSansMedium&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black">It is my hope we can quickly resolve this in a fair way. If the process is set up to produce an unfair,</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-autospace:none"><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;FreightSansMedium&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black">one-sided result, we are prepared to mobilize our delegates to force as many votes as necessary</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-autospace:none"><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;FreightSansMedium&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black">to amend the platform and rules on the floor of the convention.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
