<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-autospace:none"><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;FreightSansMedium&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black">Thank you in advance for your help in establishing standing committees that are fair and</span><o:p></o:p></p>
